caption.title: Infectivity of normalized pseudoparticles.
caption.p: Infectivity is presented as the mean ± SD percentage of infected cells ( n = 4). Blue bars, infectivity of pseudoparticles comprising native combinations of HA and NA (09H1::09N1 and AH H5::AH N1); gray bars, infectivity of mismatched pseudoparticles; white bars, infectivity of pseudoparticles in the presence of oseltamivir.
